http://www.panda.org:80/news/wwfnews/WWF_News_Winter/policy.htm 204.243.96.56 19970217022947 text/html 3275
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Monday, 17-Feb-97 02:25:37 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 08-May-96 14:13:56 GMT
Content-length: 3089
Content-type: text/html
