<H2>Registration form</H2>
<P><I></I>
<P>
<P>Non-govermental Organisations who would like to register their support for this Code and their willingness to incorporate its principles into their work should fill in the form below and return it to <BR>
<B>The Disaster Policy Department,</B><BR>
<B>The International Federation of Red Cross and Red Crescent Societies,</B><BR>
<B>PO Box 372,</B><BR>
<B>1211 Geneva 19</B><BR>
<B>Switzerland.</B><BR>

<P><I>We would like to register our support for the Code of Conduct and will endeavour to incorporate its principles into our work. </I><BR>

