<P>
<H2>Resolutions of the 26th International Conference of the Red Cross and Red Crescent :  Resolution 8</H2>
<P><I></I>
<P>
<P>
<H3><B>Date and place of the 27th International Conference of the Red Cross and Red Crescent</B></H3>
<P>
<P>The 26th International Conference of the Red Cross and Red Crescent,<BR>

<P><I>decides</I> to hold the 27th International Conference in 1999, the date and place to be decided by the Standing Commission of the Red Cross and Red Crescent.<BR>

