</TD></TR></TABLE>

<P><IMG SRC="/gifsICRC/Separator_Line_ICRC.gif" BORDER=0><BR>

<P>
<P>
<H2>D. Support for the Movement</H2>
<P><I></I>
<P>
<P>For over 130 years the Movement has lent neutral, impartial and independent assistance to the victims of war and disaster. Throughout that time it has built up a unique reputation and position within the international community, a reputation and position which are especially relevant in today's world of internal strife and increasing violence. The Movement exists, and is able to render assistance by virtue of the trust put in it and the support it gets from governments and the public. This support will be needed as much in the future as it has ever been.<BR>

