<HEAD>
<TITLE> From the end of the Second World War to the dawn of the third millennium : the activities of the International Committee of the Red Cross during the Cold War<BR>
and its aftermath: 1945-1995 </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>

<P>
<P>
<P>
<TABLE>
<TR valign=top><TD>
<P><IMG SRC="/gifsICRC/IconICRC.gif" ALIGN=left HSPACE=10></TD><TD>
